      "speaker_name": "段仇世",
      "listener": "char_yang_hua",
      "text": "华儿，我不行啦，你快去帮忙你的三师父吧。",
      "tone": "沉声",
      "chapter": 3
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_duan_chou_shi",
      "speaker_name": "段仇世",
      "listener": "char_yang_hua",
      "text": "你还不去。",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 3
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yang_hua",
      "speaker_name": "杨华",
      "listener": "char_dan_qiu_sheng",
      "text": "师父，你、你们……",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 3
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_dan_qiu_sheng",
      "speaker_name": "丹丘生",
      "listener": "char_yang_hua",
      "text": "别说话。",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 3
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_dan_qiu_sheng",
      "speaker_name": "丹丘生",
      "listener": "char_yang_hua",
      "text": "好了，华儿这条小命总算捡回来了。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 3
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yang_hua",
      "speaker_name": "杨华",
      "listener": "char_dan_qiu_sheng",
      "text": "师父，你怎么啦？",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 3
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_dan_qiu_sheng",
      "speaker_name": "丹丘生",
      "listener": "char_yang_hua",
      "text": "你放心，阳继孟所受的伤决不在我之下，我若是活不成，这魔头也是决计不能活在世上！",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 3
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yang_hua",
      "speaker_name": "杨华",
      "listener": "char_dan_qiu_sheng",
      "text": "不，不，师父，你、你们不、不能死！",
      "tone": "恐惧",
      "chapter": 3
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_dan_qiu_sheng",
      "speaker_name": "丹丘生",
      "listener": "char_yang_hua",
      "text": "人谁无死？只要死而无憾，那就是值得了。如今没有多少时候了，你附耳过来，我有话吩咐你。",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 3
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_dan_qiu_sheng",
      "speaker_name": "丹丘生",
      "listener": "char_yang_hua",
      "text": "我身上有我毕生心血写成的本派武学精义，我本想托你的二帅父带给本派掌门的，现在只能传给你了。但掌门师叔是不会认你作本派弟子的，你也不必交给他们，就自己另开一派吧。还有……",
      "tone": "沉声",
      "chapter": 3
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_duan_chou_shi",
      "speaker_name": "段仇世",
      "listener": "char_yang_hua",
      "text": "记着，要练成盂家刀法。孟元超，他，他是你的……",
      "tone": "痛苦",
      "chapter": 3
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yang_hua",
      "speaker_name": "杨华",
      "listener": "char_duan_chou_shi",
      "text": "孟元超是我的什么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 3
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yang_hua",
      "speaker_name": "杨华",
      "listener": "char_dan_qiu_sheng",
      "text": "三师父，三师父！",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 3
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yang_hua",
      "speaker_name": "杨华",
      "listener": "char_dan_qiu_sheng",
      "text": "三师父，三师父，你不是还有话要和我说么？",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 3
    }
